Ryan Dalforno

    • About Me:

    Im a Master of Public Health candidate at Vanderbilt developing skills in environmental health research and project implementation. My experience and interests involve quantifying, addressing, and communicating population-level health concerns resulting from pollution, environmental alteration, and climate change. I plan to start pursuing a doctoral degree in environmental health sciences in August 2023.
